cu.explanation_en: Setting GNB_PORT_FOR_S1U to 99999 (valid range 1024-65535, but typically lower) will cause port configuration validation failure and prevent S1-U interface establishment.

du.explanation_en: Setting dl_frequencyBand to 999 (invalid band number) will cause frequency band configuration validation failure and prevent cell setup.
du.explanation_zh: 將 dl_frequencyBand 設定為 999（無效頻帶編號）會導致頻帶配置驗證失敗，並阻止小區設置。
